Expanded compliance research and documentation review for Telepathic Immortal project.

Reviewed and aligned project disclosures with the following U.S. and international
regulatory, standards, and best-practice frameworks (non-exhaustive, ongoing):

— U.S. FEDERAL & STATE PRIVACY / CONSUMER PROTECTION —

• Federal Trade Commission (FTC)
  - Privacy & Data Security Guidance
  - Truth in Advertising principles as applied to software disclosures
  - Disclosures 101 (clear and conspicuous notice standards)
  - Dark Patterns and consent clarity guidance
  - Consumer representations regarding audio, microphone, and sensor access

• Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA)
  - FTC consumer guidance and statutory interpretation
  - Child-directed vs general audience classification
  - No-collection, no-retention exemption analysis
  - Real-time, local-only processing considerations
  - Explicit children’s use disclosures without personal data collection

